OL,3,CAnger over 'lack of progress' three
OL,4,Cyears on from Midhurst hotel fire
OL,6,FThree years since a fire burnt down a
OL,7,F17th century hotel in Midhurst,
OL,8,Fthere's anger from local business
OL,9,Fowners and residents over a lack of
OL,10,Fprogress.
OL,12,FMore than 30 people were evacuated
OL,13,Ffrom the coaching inn as 14 fire crews
OL,14,Fworked to tackle the blaze in March
OL,15,F2023.
OL,17,FIndependent businesses say the boarded
OL,18,FAngel Inn and fenced off pathway is a
OL,19,F'real scar on the landscape of the
OL,20,Ftown'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
