PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773765951
OL,3,CAnger over 'lack of progress' three
OL,4,Cyears on from Midhurst hotel fire
OL,6,FA cross-organisational working group,
OL,7,Fincluding the site owners, County
OL,8,FCouncil, Town Council, and South Downs
OL,9,FNational Park Authority, has been
OL,10,Fworking to help unlock development so
OL,11,Fthe site can be brought back into use
OL,12,Fas soon as possible.
OL,14,FHoardings protecting the decaying wall
OL,15,Fhave closed off large sections of
OL,16,FNorth Street - which businesses say
OL,17,Fhave had a noticeable impact on
OL,18,Ffootfall in the town.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
