PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773765951
OL,3,CAnger over 'lack of progress' three
OL,4,Cyears on from Midhurst hotel fire
OL,6,FAnthony Curl, manager of Midhurst
OL,7,FPharmacy, said: "It's like a blot on
OL,8,Fthe landscape. It pretty much divides
OL,9,Fthe town in half.
OL,11,F"I think people avoid the town because
OL,12,Fit's not a great building to look at.
OL,13,FAnd also, we don't get much feedback
OL,14,Fon what's going on, people come in
OL,15,Fhere expecting us to know what's
OL,16,Fhappening."
OL,26,@xD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
