PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773765951
OL,3,CAnger over 'lack of progress' three
OL,4,Cyears on from Midhurst hotel fire
OL,6,FPeople living near the Angel Inn have
OL,7,Freported problems selling their
OL,8,Fproperties or facing difficulties
OL,9,Faccessing their homes behind the fire
OL,10,Fdamaged buildings.
OL,12,FAndrew Griffith, who is the
OL,13,FConservative MP for Arundel and the
OL,14,FSouth Downs, is holding a resident's
OL,15,Fsurvey asking for their opinion of the
OL,16,Ffire-damaged site.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773765951
OL,3,CAnger over 'lack of progress' three
OL,4,Cyears on from Midhurst hotel fire
OL,6,FHe said: "This is a big visitor
OL,7,Feconomy and people aren't coming as
OL,8,Foften as they were. It's a difficult
OL,9,Ftime for high streets anyway across
OL,10,Fthe country. But imagine having that
OL,11,Fin the middle of your high street for
OL,12,Fthree years. You can't as a
OL,13,Fpedestrian, walk along that side of
OL,14,Fthe road. It's time for some action."
OL,16,FThe building is Grade II listed with
OL,17,FHistoric England and much of the
OL,18,Fbuilding dates back to the 18th
OL,19,Fcentury, with parts being renovated in
OL,20,Fthe 19th century.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773765951
OL,3,CAnger over 'lack of progress' three
OL,4,Cyears on from Midhurst hotel fire
OL,6,FThe South Downs National Park, which
OL,7,Fis the Local Planning Authority, say
OL,8,Fthe delay is due to a number of
OL,9,Freasons: the site is both listed,
OL,10,Fwithin a Conservation Area, and it's
OL,11,Ftaken time for insurers to agree a
OL,12,Fsettlement.
OL,14,FThe authority said: "We share
OL,15,Feverybody's frustrations about the
OL,16,Famount of time that has now passed
OL,17,Fsince the blaze, not least as our
OL,18,Fprimary business location is in the
OL,19,Ftown.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773765951
OL,3,CAnger over 'lack of progress' three
OL,4,Cyears on from Midhurst hotel fire
OL,6,F"We are delighted that a specialist
OL,7,Fpractice is now advising the owners
OL,8,Fand they have come forward with a
OL,9,Fbasic proposal for the fire-damaged
OL,10,Fbuildings that include the Angel Inn
OL,11,Fsite.
OL,13,F"This is the first time we have been
OL,14,Fclose to receiving a bona fide
OL,15,Fplanning application in the three
OL,16,Fyears since the fire, despite the
OL,17,Fefforts of all parties involved.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773765951
OL,3,CAnger over 'lack of progress' three
OL,4,Cyears on from Midhurst hotel fire
OL,6,F"The exact details of the proposals
OL,7,Fare still being finalised by the
OL,8,Fowners and their advisers and they
OL,9,Finclude options to demolish some
OL,10,Felements of the building, while
OL,11,Fretaining or reusing others.
OL,13,F"We are hopeful that the proposal can
OL,14,Fbe finalised in the coming weeks and
OL,15,Fbe submitted as a full planning
OL,16,Fapplication as soon as possible."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
